    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> with 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p>",
