    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced shallot </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
