      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>tomato stock </strong>and <strong>soft cheese </strong>to the pan and cook for 2-3 min further or until the sauce has thickened</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
