    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, add the <strong>cooked conchiglie </strong>and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>grated cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy corn conchiglie</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
